descriptionHtml:
first i would like to thank [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/2531318]FrankFamily[/url] for his help because without his help i could not finish this work so  - THANK YOU  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/2531318]FrankFamily[/url] - 

This sword is inspired by the Clontarf sword by Albion sword , i have tried to make it exactly like the original one , but i am new to moding , actually this is my second mod , i hope i am getting better . 
The sword is craft able at any forge 
It has a 4K texture
all the notices about this mod are much appreciated

thanks to every one who endorsed & download my previous mod  . 
 

program used :
- cinema 4D 
- Photoshop
